headline.print_headline: Quakes Destroy or Damage 83 Houses in Philippines
headline.main: Quakes Destroy or Damage 83 Houses in Philippines

lead_paragraph: A series of earthquakes destroyed 17 houses and damaged 66 others Saturday in a southern Philippine town, slightly injuring three people, officials said.
